# Orby feature freeze (flying sphere)

**FROZEN** since 2026-05-30 until product explicitly lifts it. See `Docs/Features/Shrine/Orby_FEATURE_FREEZE.md`.

## Allowed

- Bug fixes restoring documented shipped behavior
- Tests and doc updates aligned with shipped behavior
- Zero–visual-change dependency/security fixes

## Not allowed without explicit product approval

- New moods, phases, microbehaviors, particles, or interactions
- Visual redesign (eyes, mouth, cosmic material, blush, hover, wake/sleep rituals)
- New permissions or persistence
- Scope beyond the macOS floating orb face

When asked for Orby features during freeze: implement only if clearly a **bugfix** for shipped spec; otherwise note the freeze and ask for lift confirmation.
